    "original": "We shall earn the trust of a noble house and become their ally. Surely they will\nshare the fruits of their well-stocked armories with good friends.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "this.m.ButtonText = \"We shall earn the trust of a noble house and become their ally. Surely they will\\nshare the fruits of their well-stocked armories with good friends.\""
